1. Basic Level
Write a program to print numbers from 1 to 10 using a for loop.
Create a program to display the first 10 natural numbers using a while loop.
Print all even numbers from 1 to 50 using a for loop.
Write a program to calculate the sum of the first 10 natural numbers using a loop.
Display a multiplication table for a given number using a do-while loop.
Check if a number is prime by iterating through potential divisors.
Write a program to reverse the digits of an integer using a while loop.

2. Intermediate Level
Print the Fibonacci series up to n terms using a loop.
Display all prime numbers between 1 and 100 using nested loops.
Write a program to find the factorial of a given number using a loop.
Implement a program to find the greatest common divisor (GCD) of two numbers using a loop.
Create a pattern like this using nested loops:
